assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: AZ-COM MARUWA Holdings Inc. provides logistics services. The company's 3PL services include cold food, pharmaceutical medical, and room temperature logistics services. It is also involved in the collection and transportation of industrial waste; storage of documents; and provision of trucking, container transport, and logistics consulting services. The company was formerly known as Maruwa Unyu Kikan Co.,Ltd. The company was founded in 1970 and is headquartered in Yoshikawa, Japan.
